get sources
git clone https://olamy@github.com/olamy/robot-puzzle.git

You need Apache Maven and jdk 1.7

building project :
cd robot-puzzle && mvn clean test

or using a shaded jar : 
* with input from a file
  mvn clean install && java -jar target/robot-1.0-SNAPSHOT.jar -f src/test/resources/robot-order.txt
* with input from interactive cli
  mvn clean install && java -jar target/robot-1.0-SNAPSHOT.jar
